          <span class="related-label">Artwork</span>
          <span class="related-title">SRF Phase Transition Diagram</span>
          <span class="related-desc">The thermodynamics lens — regulation as water changing state under heat.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/artwork/ad-converter/" class="related-link">
          <span class="related-label">Artwork</span>
          <span class="related-title">The A/D Converter</span>
          <span class="related-desc">The signal processing lens — perception as quantization at variable bit depth.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/halmetoja-model/" class="related-link">
          <span class="related-label">Framework</span>
          <span class="related-title">The Halmetoja Model</span>
          <span class="related-desc">The psychological framework these engineering models describe.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/research/" class="related-link">
          <span class="related-label">Research</span>
          <span class="related-title">Structural Regulation Framework (SRF)</span>
          <span class="related-desc">The formal academic paper with operational definitions and testable hypotheses.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .piece-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back:hover { color: var(--text); }

  .piece-image {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
  }
  .piece-image img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  h1 { margin: 0 0 0.25rem; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .piece-subtitle { margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
  h2 { margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  h3 { margin: 0 0 0.4rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); }
  p { line-height: 1.75; color: var(--muted); }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  li strong { color: var(--text); }

  .component {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .component p { margin: 0; }

  .insight {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .related {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .related-link {
    display: block;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--surface);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.12s ease, border-color 0.12s ease, background 0.12s ease;
  }

  .related-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    background: var(--panel);
  }

  .related-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .related-title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .related-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .related { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
